        "action": "Remove the requirement of mandatory religious acts in public schools.",
        "additional_details": "The article states \"While faith schools are permitted to hold acts of worship in accordance with their religious character, in secular schools the worship must be wholly & mainly of a Christian character.\" \r\n\r\nhttps://www.independent.co.uk/news/education/education-news/mandatory-christian-prayers-in-schools-should-be-axed-academics-say-a6762256.html viewed: 13th of October 2018.\r\n\r\nIn Wales and England pupils are able to opt out, but they still sit and watch.",
